GameLogic

* Keeps Score

* Determines Hit/Miss

* Determines if ships are sunk

* Knows placement of all ships

* Checks if placement of ship is valid

* Processes fire orders from player and AI


Player View

* Guides player in ship placement

* Allows player to issue fire order


GameGrid

* Displays AI and Player grids

* is updated by Game Loop Manager


AI View

* Randomly places ships

* Sends guess to Game Logic


Game Manager

* manages turns between AI and Player

* determines when to display grid

* shuts game down







